hcc_text: East 149th Street is a pedestrian high crash corridor (top 10% for pedestrian deaths and serious injuries per mile in the Bronx)
info: At East 149th Street at Third Avenue, Willis Avenue and Melrose Avenue, there were 5 deaths and severe injuries in crashes between 2008 and 2012.
